    R->>AS: find by api_source_id
    alt api_source_id valid
        R->>AS: find model by model_id
        alt model_id found
            R->>M: return ModelConfig(provider, model_id, params)
        else model_id not found (removed/renamed)
            R->>M: fallback to AS.models[0]
            Note over R: Log warning: model_id not found
        end
    else api_source_id invalid
        R->>AS: use first ApiSource
        R->>M: fallback to AS.models[0]
        Note over R: Log warning: api_source not found
    end
```

### Trigger Condition
`resolve_model()` is called whenever an agent is spawned: relay pipeline step, chat turn, or errand dispatch.

### Data Flow
```
[AgentConfig: api_source_id + model_id] → [lookup ApiSource] → [find ModelDefinition by id] → [ModelConfig]
```

