By storing `model_id` instead of `model_tier`, we eliminate the entire downgrade-walk logic (current lines 548-586) and give users direct control. The tier tag remains for UX convenience — showing "Mid" next to "claude-sonnet-4-20250514" helps users understand cost/capability without forcing them into a rigid hierarchy.

